Subject: Re: [VB] How do you remove oil filler piece?

I have removed several of these nuts
easily with the improvised tool ( $ free )
every one had a thin paper gasket.
I have discovered that a SP intake
copper ring gasket is the same ID
and will crush nicely for the same
result.
Dave \X/

